## 2021-01-10

Linode VPS -- 1GB Ram, 1CPU, Ubuntu 20.04.1 LTS


Added A Record in domain DNS to point to server ip : 198.74.51.225

	`A  forum.shiny.ooo  198.74.51.225  1798`


Check to see if DNS is resolving to ip

```
